temperatures

Class Temperature

  • java.lang.Object
    • temperatures.Temperature

  • public class Temperature
extends java.lang.Object

    Uses an input text file (inFile) to instantiate temperature information in a two-dimensional array and then writes the data formatted to a new text file with various temperature facts for the year.

    Since:
    1.0 (04/18/2017)
    Version:
    1.0.1 (01/13/2019)
    Author:
    Brady Lange - LinkedIn

    • Field Detail

      • temps

        private double[][] temps
        Temperature's for each month - Average High/Low for 12 months. Row One: High Temperature, Row Two: Low Temperature. Column one to twelve are the months from January to December.
